The paper deals with wireless power transfer (WPT) and data transmission over fading channels, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). The paper also discusses optimization and control policies for maximizing throughput, which falls under systems and control (cs.SY). The paper uses Bayesian inference as a reinforcement learning method for optimizing sensing resolution, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
